  "special": {
    "title": "In. Not unlike Errol.",
    "description": "Consumes 3 rounds to fire 8 slow pellets. After a short distance, the spread opens into a horizontal bird-like pattern. While aiming, it fires a Dahl burst, with an extra burst shot if it has a Dahl stock."
  },
  "notes": "The extra pellets are not shown on the item card, and each pellet receives full amp damage. Projectile speed can be boosted by the Flying prefix, Maya's Accelerate, or Zer0's Vel0city. It is more ammo-efficient per pellet than the Lascaux, and the fixed spread can help at range against large, slow targets, though the lower fire rate hurts sustained damage somewhat. Hidden parts can alter the stats, and the displayed prefix can override others. A Dahl stock raises the aimed burst from 3 to 4 rounds. On Gaige, Anarchy has relatively little effect, while Close Enough can merge ricochets and actually reduce total output.",
